Package: ccze
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: A roboust, modular log coloriser.
 CCZE is a roboust and modular log colorizer, with plugins for apm,
 exim, fetchmail, httpd, postfix, procmail, squid, syslog, ulogd,
 vsftpd, xferlog and more.

Package: colorize
Architecture: all
Depends: ccze
Description: Dummy package for transition to ccze.
 This dummy package provides a transition from colorize to ccze, which
 supersedes it.
 .
 After the upgrade completed, this package may be safely removed.
